io.werval.test

Class WervalTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.werval.test.WervalTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpBuilders, HttpBuildersSPI, WervalTestSupport
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CacheTest, TemplatesTest 

    public class WervalTest
extends Object
implements WervalTestSupport
    Base Werval JUnit Test.

    Activate/Passivate Werval Application in test mode around each JUnit test method.

    By default, configuration is loaded from the application.conf file. Override the configurationResourceName() method to provide your own test configuration.

    By default, routes are loaded from the routes.conf file. Override the routesProvider() method to provide your own test routes.
